description:
BrM:  Table storing Ericsson-specific attributes of Base Station measurements (BrM) data for a specific time and location.

dateTime: Timestamp of the measurement.
Area_Name: Name of the geographic area where the measurement was taken (e.g., NR cell in Balikpapan).
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  An identifier (appears constant in sample data, requires further investigation).
vsDataType: Type of data (always 'vsDataBrM' in sample).
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the Ericsson-specific data format.
BrM.brMId:  ID of the BrM record.
BrM.exportPackageLabelPrefix: Prefix for export package labeling (empty in sample).
